<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: left;"><span style="text-align: -webkit-auto;">You may notice that&nbsp;sometimes long commands doesn't be wrapped when&nbsp;using bash in gnome-terminal. However, it's considered to be a bug of gnome-terminal. the solution is pretty simple: use system default font! which is configurable in preference dialog.</span></div>


